612
00:28:36,060 --> 00:28:38,800
Mr. Lu wants you to...

613
00:28:41,110 --> 00:28:41,790
Where is he?

614
00:28:41,790 --> 00:28:43,480
Miss Guooo...

615
00:28:43,480 --> 00:28:44,960
-Mr. Lu. Mr. Lu
-Let go of me!

616
00:28:44,960 --> 00:28:47,890
