651
00:30:46,720 --> 00:30:47,510
Business

652
00:30:48,290 --> 00:30:49,160
and shares.

653
00:30:50,480 --> 00:30:51,720
That's all you know?

654
00:30:52,790 --> 00:30:54,960
This is the only way

655
00:30:54,960 --> 00:30:56,760
