670
00:31:32,100 --> 00:31:33,830
But the wedding has just ended.

671
00:31:34,720 --> 00:31:36,200
Grandpa doesn't want

672
00:31:36,200 --> 00:31:38,030
our relationship

673
00:31:39,000 --> 00:31:39,960
