674
00:31:55,920 --> 00:31:56,680
Mr. Lu.

675
00:31:56,790 --> 00:31:58,270
Keep an eye on him.

676
00:31:58,270 --> 00:31:59,920
No matter what you do,

677
00:31:59,980 --> 00:32:01,110
