717
00:34:27,110 --> 00:34:28,440
When we were in Yicheng.

718
00:34:31,300 --> 00:34:33,429
He said he wanted to
make a deal with me.

719
00:34:35,030 --> 00:34:36,630
As long as I return you to him,

720
00:34:38,159 --> 00:34:39,760
