I just want to be with you.

730
00:35:35,960 --> 00:35:37,090
We will be together.

731
00:35:37,920 --> 00:35:39,840
We will always,

732
00:35:39,840 --> 00:35:40,960
always,

733
00:35:40,960 --> 00:35:42,090
always be together.

734
